    <div class="main review-item" id="5708410">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5708410/" class="title-link">讀史書不讀此書等於沒讀過</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5708410"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/53040554/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u53040554-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/53040554/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">仁義中國</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-12-22"
      class="main-meta">2012-12-22 09:07:12</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5708410_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  本書極其優秀，是我讀過最好的史評之一，和王船山先生的《讀通鑒論》可以說同等價值。  關鍵是其總結了不少歷史規律。還有很多縱向對比。例如其論寒士就很有見解。論明史等等，讀了此書，無數的規律可以參考。  趙翼的其他書也很不錯。陔餘叢考考據也很詳實，我非常喜愛。

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5708410/#comments">(1回应)</a>
