            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/diaohui/" class=" " title="載酒江湖">載酒江湖</a>
                (工作随时努力，生活随遇而安。)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="20202237">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">然亦可见汉初起兵，即令诸将各立简牍，以纪劳绩，无枉无滥，所以能得人死力，以定大业也。</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/20202237/">(<span class="">1回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
